title: Nadal Beats Fognini to Reach Final of China Open
text:
Published By: NYTimes Tennis - Today 
Rafael Nadal reached his first hard-court final in more than a year on Saturday, beating Fabio Fognini 7-5, 6-3 in the China Open semifinals...
